  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Continental buffet breakfast for 7 mornings with hot option provided on 6 mornings per week†</li>
<li>Afternoon tea and coffee with cake &amp; savoury treat on 6 days†</li>
<li>3 course buffet dinner served 6 days, including pre-dinner glass of prosecco and canapés, a choice of complimentary wine &amp; tea/coffee†</li>
<li><span>Complimentary tea &amp; coffee available throughout the day</span></li>
<li>Special celebration menus on Christmas Day &amp; New Year's Eve<span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><span>†(Breakfast hot option, afternoon tea &amp; dinner is 6 days per week due to Chalet Hotel staff's day off)</span></p>
